Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we managed to \Nbreak through the blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish he'd hurry up and fill us \Nin on the next part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That boy always waits until \Nthe last second to tell—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-What on earth are you wearing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal? I'm \Nbroiling in this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your private space!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn to tell the difference—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nag, nag, nag...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Renbokoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know she has the same \Nlast name as Satomi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-chan, we want to thank \Nyou for coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about showing us your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't interact through \Ntexting forever, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk to Akira, \Nyou'll do it through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But we're pilots who fight side \Nby side, so why won't she...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my duty to keep Akira safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.72,0:01:04.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As her family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about during a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have to go through you even then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination is Earthspace,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old JIOR territory, Ookuma district.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we're starting an \Noperation to retake JIOR!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a force recon, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go changing the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, they're pretty \Nmuch the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Descents to Earth are conducted \Nusing Follow Rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we borrow a drop shuttle in the \Nentrance space and dock with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all we have to do is follow \Ninstructions and proceed down the rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, all we have to do is \Ndive down through those rings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guidance inside the ring is \Nhandled automatically, so even a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bunch of amateurs shouldn't \Nhave a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing that worries me is \Nthat you need clearance for a drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or so he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this stuff is over my \Nhead, so I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:03:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you show us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While there's still time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, all we can do is fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a curse, but it's \Nalso a power that we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having trouble swallowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, I saw her myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an ultra-hot redhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ultra-hot girl recluses \Nare the two-dimensional kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not this one, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira Renbokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the fact that \NUnit 6's pilot is the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,legendary Little Witch like \Nsomething out of a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that legend is true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That she hacked the entrance exam to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the national university's \Nhigh school affiliate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're not talking about some \NS-class security level here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she really did that, she'd be a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that was the cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the bullying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that hacker \Nwas your little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you coddle her so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her own actions led her to be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bullied and become a recluse,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she brought it all on herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi! Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everybody tells me that my food doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:28.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,look very appetizing, but \Ntrust me, it's delicious!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But putting soy-pickled vegetables \Non wafers is a bit strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trust me, it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:34.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my word for it and give it a try!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's all kinds of \Npickled vegetables,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:41.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but the ones I recommend are the \Ntraditional JIOR Kurumaya recipe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're a thing of beauty!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're great with dinner, \Nbut they're so good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,that I figured they could \Nbe used with snacks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're awesome with \Npicked veggies on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko asked me to look out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said you're a good person, \Nbut not used to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shoko-chan did?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're friends with Shoko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes you friends with me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"The friend of my friend is my friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that's what Shoko would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F-Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi Renbokoji
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You hate your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-He never tried to help \Nme then, so why try to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-That "family" stuff. \NSelf-serving crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate it. Nothing but bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memories... Just be happy you have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have any, \Nyou can't even be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yours are bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we reach JIOR... reach Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will I be able to remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty as a picture, Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get a little \Nexercise yourself, Q-vier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but I'll pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where did H-neun go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's been playing hooky all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's this total straight-arrow \Nwith bobbed hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is so uptight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the kid is obnoxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You always sound like you're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How has that boy with \Nglasses been lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But enough about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the title of that \Nmovie you were talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take me someplace \Nwith a view of the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would the beach be too public?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or would a secluded place be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To have a private conversation, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you've been \Ntailing me since this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I call in that rain check?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we get some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Docking with shuttle complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Handing off to Follow Ring guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please begin transfer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pass validity confirmed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are cleared to enter port.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Customs inspection complete.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Opening Follow Gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a pleasant flight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, this one's an unscheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was the story with those \Nunscheduled passengers?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The usual line-cutters.\N "Special clearance from the authorities."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, again? Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it went according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A passenger liner bound for New Guinea
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and three JIOR Mail \NSteamer cargo ships...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one is a private jet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To disguise our landing time, \Nthe cargo ships would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can make out all of \Nthat? That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's always been your field \Nof expertise, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Communications frequency match!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a match for the spacecraft \Nthat launched from Module 77!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All hands to battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them land on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Dorssian navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did they find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If our communications \Nfrequency is detected,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's the obvious outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're... You're saying that I did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said there \Nwouldn't be any combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Securing the ship's flight \Npath has top priority.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we leave the rings, \Nour descent will fail!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A holding action until \Nwe begin reentry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let them near the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:01.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Assume that if we take a \Nsingle hit, it's all over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All units, don't stray \Ntoo far from the ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a whole lot of warnings!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, one came at us from underneath!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which do we attack?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both of them, obviously!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The one below us is a \Nspecial-spec Ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I brought you \Nsome rice porridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. I'm okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you have a terrible fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not I get \Ninto the best school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hinges on this one test.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take any time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do this... I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything other than a national \Nschool is unthinkable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that clear, Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be one of the winners?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you end up a loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all decided here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pass... I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, my heat levels \Nare almost critical!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are we supposed to do?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't take much more of this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go down there and \Nbeat the crap out of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.30,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.58,0:13:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you go any further from \Nthe ship and can't return,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your heat levels will \Nmax out in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is that guy working just fine?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're modified versions \Nthat have been attached
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to in-atmosphere shuttles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as that is not destroyed, they \Nare capable of unassisted reentry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move closer to the ship. \NYou're all nearly maxed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada! Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I do, we're history \Nif we take one hit, remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yamada! Come back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, once I take this guy out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All because of me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're sitting ducks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.64,0:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other one's coming \Nin for another pass!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Professor! It's just this \None, but it's good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect! Nice work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tokishima, do you read me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Care to try out a Familiar?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impact Booster, docking sequence engage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heat dump complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! He destroyed it in one blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Recall Tokishima immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll begin reentry any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, grab Akira! Retrieve Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 6 is too far away from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that other \Ntime all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I go and do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I did, he would never...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.11,OS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JIOR National University High Schoo\Nl 66th Annual Entrance Exam Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're Akira-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you a few \Nquestions, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see here that you're scheduled \Nto take the exam today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't ask her to hack into \Nthe exam test sheet, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why she \Nwould do such a thing, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.59,0:19:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he cares \Nif I live or die anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move us over to Akira. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 1, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you think you're doing?\N Return at once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand by and \Nwatch one of us die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm saving her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sentimental fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't compatible \Nwith aftermarket parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My controls, they're—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:19:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto! Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Change the ship's \Ntrajectory! Save Akira!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we override our trajectory \Nnow, this ship will burn up too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you're just going to let her die?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I let this chance pass by,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,when will I ever get another to \Nmake things right with Akira?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time, I'm gonna protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As her big brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A transmission from Unit 6? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are... ground control \Nradio transmissions?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's hacking them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hacking them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It means that even if this \Nship veers off course,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we'd still be able to make reentry \Nif we locked onto one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Akira's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's calling out to me! \NAsking me to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pick out appropriate \Nguidance from that mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible! Not \Nfrom all that noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make out anything \Nthey're saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! I can't make anything out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alter heading... to 10 \No'clock, 40 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adjust entry angle... to 27 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To the north-northeast...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi? You can...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call out the instructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take the ship's controls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to jeopardize everything \Njust to save your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we do nothing, it will \Nmean losing two Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that throw a \Nwrench in your plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leaders have to be prepared \Nto show a firm hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need Haruto's abilities, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need someone who can
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make the reentry work even \Nafter we go off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:21:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one with \Nthe skill to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:21:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't turn a deaf ear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All this time, I've \Npretended not to hear you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pretended not to see you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't hide from it anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.11,0:22:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The crime and the punishment, \Nwe'll take them on together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're family!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Units 1 and 6 are aboard the shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akira! Are you okay?! You're okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking so much, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes, they...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:23:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- L-elf. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.44,0:24:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did you set us down?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We went off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're inside Dorssian territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.41,0:24:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 15, \N"Return to Karlstein."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system that will expose \Nthe truth of the world.